9 201     Touches me deeper than you can imagine.
9 202   CLARENCE. I know it pleaseth neither of us well.
9 203   GLOUCESTER. Well, your imprisonment shall not be long;
9 204     I will deliver or else lie for you.
9 205     Meantime, have patience.
9 206   CLARENCE. I must perforce. Farewell.
